WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:03.896
Tennis superstar Maria Sharapova has been suspended from the game...

00:03.977 --> 00:05.908
...after a positive drug test.

00:06.125 --> 00:10.788
The International Tennis Federation said it was banning Sharapova for two years...

00:10.901 --> 00:14.815
...because she tested positive for meldonium at the Australian Open.

00:15.028 --> 00:19.684
The drug was placed on the banned substances list on January 1st.

00:20.146 --> 00:24.619
Sharapova said she had been taking it for about ten years for health issues...

00:24.703 --> 00:26.139
...and she said she will appeal.

